<kos/service/type/resource-facing> a skos:Concept ; skos:inScheme <https://w3id.org/noria/kos/service/type> ; rdfs:label "Resource Facing Service"@en, "Service Interne"@fr .

# Trouble Ticket Severity
<kos/TroubleTicket/severity/Critical> a skos:Concept ; skos:inScheme <https://w3id.org/noria/kos/TroubleTicket/severity> ; rdfs:label "Critical"@en, "Critique"@fr .
<kos/TroubleTicket/severity/Major> a skos:Concept ; skos:inScheme <https://w3id.org/noria/kos/TroubleTicket/severity> ; rdfs:label "Major"@en, "Majeur"@fr .
