# Change Request Category
<kos/ChangeRequest/category/InternalIntervention> a skos:Concept ; skos:inScheme <https://w3id.org/noria/kos/ChangeRequest/category> ; rdfs:label "Internal Intervention"@en, "Intervention Interne"@fr .
